  43. /*
  44. * pg_regfree - free an RE (generic function, punts to RE-specific function)
  45. *
  46. * Ignoring invocation with NULL is a convenience.
  47. */
  48. void
  49. ‌pg_regfree(regex_t *re)
  50. {
  51.     if (re == NULL)
  52.         return;
  53.     (*((struct fns *) re->re_fns)->free) (re);
  54. }
